jobInfo.postDescription:
软件工程师 Software Engineer
POSITION RESPONSIBLITY 岗位职责: 
- To take part to the products development. 产品开发
- To give the technical support to other engineering group. 支持工程团队的工作
- To follow Company Product Development Standard and Software development standard. 遵循公司产品开发标准和软件开发标准
- To use configuration management tool to maintain quality records. 使用配置管理工具维护质量记录
- To analyze the customers requirements and generate Software Requirement Specification. 分析客户需求并生成软件需求规范
- To design and create software following company coding standard. 根据公司编码标准设计和开发软件
- To give the technical support to the project, hardware, software validation and other functional team. 为项目、硬件、软件验证和其他功能团队提供技术支持
- To participate to the product/project team meeting. 参加产品/项目团队会议
- To take part in the product improvement (tooling improvement, tests sequence….). 参与产品改进(模具改进，测试顺序....) 等
（薪资再洽谈）
REQUIRED QUALIFICATIONS 岗位要求:
- Diploma: Bachelor or above in Electronic Engineering, Computer Science or related engineering. 本科/学士及以上学历（电子工程、计算机技术或其他相关专业）
- Experience in real-time embedded software environment. 有实时嵌入式软件开发经验
- Ability to work effectively within a global team. 
- Fluent English (workable in writing, reading, listening, speaking). 
- Willing to work outside or biz trip.
